// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1073 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 05a46174-396a-5cd9-918f-c8238c918ed3

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:5*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:6*" or process.executable like~ "*redhat/ubi9:*")
